#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.150"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.150:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.150:0.2"
msgid "15. Maṅgalavagga"
msgstr "15. Good Fortune"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.150:0.3"
msgid "150. Paṭhamakhatasutta"
msgstr "150. Broken (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.150:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ "
"upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca "
"apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"“When a foolish, incompetent, bad person has three qualities they keep "
"themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and reproved by "
"sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

msgctxt "an3.150:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.150:1.3"
msgid "Akusalena kāyakammena, akusalena vacīkammena, akusalena manokammena—"
msgstr "Unskillful deeds by way of body, speech, and mind. …"

msgctxt "an3.150:1.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bālo abyatto asappuriso "
"khataṃ upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.150:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ "
"anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca puññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent, good person has three qualities they keep "
"themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized "
"by sensible people, and they make much merit."

msgctxt "an3.150:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.150:2.3"
msgid ""
"Kusalena kāyakammena, kusalena vacīkammena, kusalena manokammena … pe …."
msgstr "Skillful deeds by way of body, speech, and mind. …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.150:2.4"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
